<!-- FEATURES SECTION -->
<section class="py-32 px-8 max-w-7xl mx-auto" id="features">
    <div class="mb-20 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-[1.75rem] font-black tracking-tight mb-4">Everything you need. Nothing you don't.</h2>
        <div class="w-16 h-1 bg-secondary mx-auto rounded-full"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="p-8 bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-2xl group hover:shadow-[0_24px_48px_-12px_rgba(28,27,27,0.04)] transition-all">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary text-3xl mb-6">grid_view</span>
            <h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-4">Interactive Schedule Grid</h4>
            <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed">A powerful time-matrix view. Drag and drop shifts, right-click for context actions, and see changes propagate in real-time via SignalR.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-8 bg-tertiary-container text-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl transform scale-105 relative z-10">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-tertiary-fixed text-3xl mb-6">auto_awesome</span>
            <h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-4">Auto-Fill Scheduling</h4>
            <p class="text-tertiary-fixed text-sm leading-relaxed">One click. That's all it takes. An evolutionary algorithm tests 50+ scenarios to find the optimal assignment for your entire schedule.</p>
            <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 animate-pulse">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-tertiary-fixed shadow-[0_0_12px_rgba(133,248,196,1)]"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-8 bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-2xl group hover:shadow-[0_24px_48px_-12px_rgba(28,27,27,0.04)] transition-all">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary text-3xl mb-6">content_cut</span>
            <h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-4">Shift Cutting &amp; Splitting</h4>
            <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed">Split shifts by time, date, weekday, or holiday. Create container templates for recurring patterns in a hierarchical tree structure.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-8 bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-2xl group hover:shadow-[0_24px_48px_-12px_rgba(28,27,27,0.04)] transition-all">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary text-3xl mb-6">event_busy</span>
            <h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-4">Absence Management</h4>
            <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed">Visual Gantt diagrams show vacation, sick leave, and custom absence types at a glance. Export to PDF with one click.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-8 bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-2xl group hover:shadow-[0_24px_48px_-12px_rgba(28,27,27,0.04)] transition-all">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary text-3xl mb-6">checklist</span>
            <h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-4">4-Stage Approval Workflow</h4>
            <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed">From Draft to Confirmed to Approved to Closed. Each stage locks further editing with group-based access control.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-8 bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-2xl group hover:shadow-[0_24px_48px_-12px_rgba(28,27,27,0.04)] transition-all">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary text-3xl mb-6">route</span>
            <h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-4">Route Optimization</h4>
            <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed">Plan deployment routes with ant colony optimization. Supports car, bicycle, walking, and mixed transport modes.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

